 <metadata>
  <name>Round The Back Of Tesco's (In Reverse)</name>
  <desc>Exit the park turning right onto Rectory Road over the roundabout then right onto Bent Lane and left onto Ostrich Lane. Left up BOR all the way past Kirkham's and over the motorway. Left onto Hardman's Rd, across the footbridge onto Tesco side of BNR. Right past TGI onto Pinfold Drive all the way around continuing straight onto Kingswood Rd up to Bury New Rd.  Cross over at the lights and run down BNR back to the start through St Mary's Park.</desc>
  <author>
   <name>Dale Richards</name>
   <link href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/108724580"/>
  </author>
  <copyright author="OpenStreetMap contributors">
   <year>2020</year>
   <license>https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright</license>
  </copyright>
  <link href="https://www.strava.com/routes/3431255266302052558"/>
 </metadata>
